<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>MoveSmart Nutrición Trail</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #080d0a;
      --panel: rgba(14, 20, 16, 0.82);
      --panel-soft: rgba(22, 31, 24, 0.72);
      --green: #92b83e;
      --green-2: #6f922d;
      --text: #f5f7f2;
      --muted: #b9c0b3;
      --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11);
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
      --radius: 26px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(6, 10, 7, 0.96) 0%, rgba(6, 10, 7, 0.82) 40%, rgba(6, 10, 7, 0.55) 100%),
        url("fondo-trail-nutricion.webp") center/cover fixed no-repeat,
        #080d0a;
    }

    .app {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 230px minmax(0, 1fr);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      padding: 28px 22px;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(5, 9, 7, 0.78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo {
      display: grid;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 42px;
    }

    .logo .mountain {
      color: var(--green);
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .logo strong {
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 0.9;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    .logo span {
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .nav a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 15px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      transition: 0.2s ease;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .nav a.active,
    .nav a:hover {
      background: rgba(146, 184, 62, 0.17);
      color: var(--green);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(146, 184, 62, 0.18);
    }

    .quote {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .quote::before {
      content: "“";
      display: block;
      color: var(--green);
      font-size: 48px;
      line-height: 0.6;
    }

    main {
      padding: 42px clamp(20px, 4vw, 62px) 42px;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 280px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 72px);
      letter-spacing: -1.5px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    }

    .date {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(146, 184, 62, 0.2);
      color: var(--green);
      border: 1px solid rgba(146, 184, 62, 0.35);
      padding: 9px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .top-tabs {
      display: flex;
      width: fit-content;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 6px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(8, 12, 9, 0.76);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .top-tabs button {
      border: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      background: transparent;
      padding: 14px 26px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .top-tabs button.active {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--green-2));
      color: #10150d;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 340px;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .section-title::after {
      content: "";
      display: block;
      width: 52px;
      height: 4px;
      background: var(--green);
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .meals {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .meal-card,
    .side-card {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .meal-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 70px minmax(0, 1fr) 190px;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 22px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .icon {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--green);
      background: rgba(146, 184, 62, 0.14);
      font-size: 26px;
    }

    .meal-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .meal-head h3 {
      font-size: 25px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .time {
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .food-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 9px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    }

    .food-list li {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 20px;
      list-style: none;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .food-list li::before {
      content: "•";
      color: var(--green);
      margin-right: 8px;
    }

    .food-list .food-name {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .food-img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 1.15 / 1;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    }

    .side {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .side-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .side-card h3 {
      font-size: 22px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .macro-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 15px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    }

    .macro-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .macro-row strong {
      color: white;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .water-drops {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 18px 0 12px;
      font-size: 25px;
    }

    .water-total {
      color: #66bdf5;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 26px;
    }

    .tip {
      background:
        linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(8, 12, 9, 0.85), rgba(8, 12, 9, 0.35)),
        url("tip-trail.webp") center/cover no-repeat;
      min-height: 210px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .tip p,
    .training p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .training h4 {
      font-size: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 22px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1050px) {
      .app {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .sidebar {
        display: none;
      }

      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .side {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      body {
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6, 10, 7, 0.45) 0%, rgba(6, 10, 7, 0.96) 310px),
          url("fondo-trail-nutricion.webp") center top/auto 360px no-repeat,
          #080d0a;
      }

      main {
        padding: 24px 14px 100px;
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: 240px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
      }

      .date {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .top-tabs {
        width: 100%;
        overflow-x: auto;
      }

      .top-tabs button {
        white-space: nowrap;
        padding: 13px 20px;
      }

      .meal-card {
        grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .meal-card .food-img {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        max-height: 210px;
      }

      .meal-head h3 {
        font-size: 21px;
      }

      .side {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div>
        <div class="logo">
          <div class="mountain">△△</div>
          <strong>MOVE<br>SMART</strong>
          <span>Nutrición Trail</span>
        </div>

        <nav class="nav">
          <a class="active" href="#">△ Hoy</a>
          <a href="#">▣ Semana</a>
          <a href="#">⚖ Equivalencias</a>
          <a href="#">☷ Notas</a>
          <a href="#">⚙ Ajustes</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="quote">Nutrir el cuerpo es potenciar el rendimiento.</div>
    </aside>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <h1>¡Hola Cami!</h1>
          <p class="date">Jueves 27 de mayo</p>
          <span class="pill">Mesociclo 2 · Trail 2026</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="top-tabs">
        <button class="active">△ HOY</button>
        <button>▣ MAÑANA</button>
        <button>▦ SEMANA</button>
        <button>⚖ EQUIVALENCIAS</button>
      </div>

      <section class="content-grid">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Tu pauta de hoy</h2>

          <div class="meals">
            <article class="meal-card">
              <div class="icon">☀</div>
              <div>
                <div class="meal-head">
                  <h3>Desayuno</h3>
                  <span class="time">07:30</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="food-list">
                  <li><span class="food-name">Avena</span><span>70 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Yogurth protein</span><span>110 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Plátano</span><span>1 ud</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Mantequilla de maní</span><span>10 g</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <img class="food-img" src="desayuno.webp" alt="Desayuno" />
            </article>

            <article class="meal-card">
              <div class="icon">⚡</div>
              <div>
                <div class="meal-head">
                  <h3>Post-entreno</h3>
                  <span class="time">09:30</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="food-list">
                  <li><span class="food-name">Suero de leche</span><span>30 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Huevo cocido</span><span>180 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Avena</span><span>30 g</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <img class="food-img" src="post-entreno.webp" alt="Post entreno" />
            </article>

            <article class="meal-card">
              <div class="icon">🍴</div>
              <div>
                <div class="meal-head">
                  <h3>Almuerzo</h3>
                  <span class="time">13:30</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="food-list">
                  <li><span class="food-name">Manzana</span><span>100 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Papa hervida</span><span>400 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Pollo</span><span>130 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Dátiles</span><span>17 g</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <img class="food-img" src="almuerzo.webp" alt="Almuerzo" />
            </article>

            <article class="meal-card">
              <div class="icon">🍃</div>
              <div>
                <div class="meal-head">
                  <h3>Colación</h3>
                  <span class="time">17:00</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="food-list">
                  <li><span class="food-name">Yogurth protein</span><span>100 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Frutos secos</span><span>15 g</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <img class="food-img" src="colacion.webp" alt="Colación" />
            </article>

            <article class="meal-card">
              <div class="icon">☾</div>
              <div>
                <div class="meal-head">
                  <h3>Cena</h3>
                  <span class="time">20:00</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="food-list">
                  <li><span class="food-name">Avena</span><span>70 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Yogurth protein</span><span>110 g</span></li>
                  <li><span class="food-name">Frutos rojos</span><span>50 g</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <img class="food-img" src="cena.webp" alt="Cena" />
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="side">
          <article class="side-card">
            <h3>Resumen del día</h3>
            <div class="macro-row"><span>Carbohidratos</span><strong>192 g</strong></div>
            <div class="macro-row"><span>Proteínas</span><strong>123 g</strong></div>
            <div class="macro-row"><span>Grasas</span><strong>31 g</strong></div>
            <div class="macro-row"><span>Calorías</span><strong>1890 kcal</strong></div>
          </article>

          <article class="side-card">
            <h3>Hidratación</h3>
            <p>Meta: 2.5 - 3 L</p>
            <div class="water-drops">💧 💧 💧 💧 💧 ◌</div>
            <p class="water-total">2.6 L</p>
          </article>

          <article class="side-card tip">
            <h3>Tip del día</h3>
            <p>Prioriza carbohidratos post cerro y buena hidratación.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="side-card training">
            <h3>Día de entrenamiento</h3>
            <h4>Trail Largo</h4>
            <p>Intensidad: Alta · Energía: Alta</p>
          </article>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <div class="footer-note">△ Cada elección te acerca a tu mejor versión.</div>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
